<ab facs="#facs_582_r2l5">den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> noch vnbekert von eẅch awſʒen ſteet etc / das haben wır <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_582_r2l6">Vnd haben mıt den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıe das angeet <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> fleıſſıg <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt / dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_582_r2l8">klagen Jr ſcheden 
<add><ab facs="#facs_582_r2l7">vaſt </ab></add> / Wıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> wi </del> kombt Jr beıd <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> eẅr einr <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_582_r2l10">des weıſʒen <expan>ſunnt<ex>ag</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_582_r2l9">ſchıerıſt </ab></add> ʒu vns . ſo ſüllt Jr <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ʒeıt ʒu vnd von Vns . für vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_582_r2l11">vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . iij tag geleyt haben / Vnd getrawen eẅch . Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_582_r2l12"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒıehet</expan> den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıe ſache niht <expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan> . Jr macht Jn des ein ende </ab>
